{"tid":668846,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應公安毆now攝影師　鄭若驊：好奇怪，好難相信會發生","createTime":"2018-05-18T03:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T04:29:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9806c87c0b0c2fcb3c1bd72f4854d48dd4a8292d","tid":668846,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/cheng-04_gtEXQ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcheng-04_gtEXQ_1200x0.png&h=4f594ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nnow新聞台駐北京記者周三（5月16日）採訪「709大抓捕」維權律師聽證會時，now攝影師被多名便衣警察暴力扣押，受傷流血，簽署悔改書後才獲釋。律政司司長鄭若驊今早被傳媒追問時，表示關注事件，政府已向相關部門反映關注，又表示很難理解會發生這種事情，「好奇怪好難相信會發生」，希望記者「安靜咗落嚟傷勢會好返」。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊今早出席公開場合時被記者要求回應，《蘋果日報》指鄭被問到事件是否有觸犯法律及記者到內地採訪等安全問題，鄭若驊未有再回應記者提問後離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/回應公安毆now攝影師-鄭若驊-好奇怪-好難相信會發生/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%AF%86now%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%AB-%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A-%E5%A5%BD%E5%A5%87%E6%80%AA-%E5%A5%BD%E9%9B%A3%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%2F&d=4RKMSrBp3%2BDoZuM3FwVM1k4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e8301c11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%AF%86now%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%AB-%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A-%E5%A5%BD%E5%A5%87%E6%80%AA-%E5%A5%BD%E9%9B%A3%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%2F&h=8e15208a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/回應公安毆now攝影師-鄭若驊-好奇怪-好難相信會發生/</a>"},{"pid":"140d62dcaf7c70e8225a351e19fc73e3b62ef406","tid":668846,"uid":156815,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:40:49.000Z","msg":"律政司僭建<br />\n好難相信會發生"},{"pid":"5a0c9d420c870d80fdd2f1f0e5388fcead38311b","tid":668846,"uid":11962,"like":0,"